Package: DEcovid
Title: Functionality for master thesis
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person("Felix", "Hofmann", , "felix.hofmann2@uzh.ch", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3891-6239"))
Description: This package provides functionality to download and preprocess data sets related to potential analyses for COVID-19 related data sets.
    It contains functionality to fetch data from various sources, preprocess this data, and fit models to it. 
    Furthermore, it also has functions to plot model fits and format tables showing coefficient estimates and standard errors.
